item.description: Negative behavior is not permitted. We should all help putting up the net if we are available. We should all be having fun! Please everyone that can help  putting up the net it would be much appreciated. This is a preseason meet-up weather permitting. If it does rain I will cancel by 5. If you are new to this we would love you to join. We usually go to a local bar after for drinks. Hope to see you there!
item.how_to_find_us: We will be there setting up the volleyball net! Let us know you are there and we will welcome you!
item.why: Alright it's that time of year again. We are going to meet at the beach again for some great volleyball. We will be putting up the net at 5:30pm and starting soon after setup.

group.name: Trailblazers- A Seacoast Singles Meetup Group
